      "text": "An Outdoor Sanctuary"
    },
    {
      "line": 11,
      "text": "Renting a Beachcomber Shack is a great way for your group to relax together during a fun evening event at Disney’s Typhoon Lagoon water park."
    },
    {
      "line": 12,
      "text": "Each Beachcomber Premium Plus accommodates a maximum of 10 Guests and includes the following amenities:"
